This repository contains:

1. AETHER overlay source (configs, DTS, build scripts, vendor tree skeleton)
   under aether-rmx3171/, device/realme/RMX3171/, docs/, .github/, scripts at
   the repo root, and the README.md / AETHER_*.md documentation files.
   These AETHER-original parts are licensed under GPL-2.0-only to be ABI-
   compatible with the Linux kernel they overlay.

2. Linux kernel base, MediaTek BSP, Samsung kernel_device_modules-6.6, and
   vendor/mediatek/kernel_modules ARE NOT redistributed in this repository.
   Users must stage those from the upstream Samsung A055F open-source kernel
   release via scripts/sync_samsung_base.sh (see README).

3. KernelSU integration source is fetched from
   https://github.com/tiann/KernelSU at build time and is licensed under
   GPL-2.0-only by its upstream maintainers.

4. AnyKernel3 packaging template is fetched from
   https://github.com/osm0sis/AnyKernel3 at build time and licensed under
   AnyKernel3's own terms.

GPL-2.0-only

